Key Match Events: England restricted Sri Lanka to 141 for eight in Sydney
Adil Rashid took his first wicket of the tournament
There was also one wicket apiece for Chris Woakes, Sam Curran and Ben Stokes
Miscellaneous Highlights: England might be without Dawid Malan in their reply due to a possible injury
Sri Lanka amassed just five fours and one six after the seventh over as England adjusted their tactics
